Let me start this with a mini-rant before I talk about development&#8230;
The saying &ldquo;You shouldn’t reinvent the wheel&rdquo; I think is complete bull and a bad choice for any reasoning without research.
Look at that saying reinvent the wheel; are we expected to think that nobody has looked at the wheel and thought &ldquo;I know what could improve this&rdquo;? When the first wheel was invented it was thought to be a rock that was carved into something circular so early humans can push things rather than drag.
